*Initial step for making an app
mkdir example
create a file index.js
install package.json and all the dependencies
inside create a public folder
create a file index.html
create a file style.css and linked it up to index.html

*Setup Websockets
install socket.io
socket setup in index.js
script link in index.html
create a file chat.js
make socket connection
console.log the socket.id

*Create the Chatroom
insert input in index.html
listen to events

*Broadcasting messages
Add User typing .....
